Here is the translation:

A new house suddenly appears beautiful, then it becomes a big deal; 
The ancient well is endless, the overflowing water is like a torrent, that's all.

Here is the translation:

It knows this, asking that, God says it will be so then; 
Then people come in accordance, bringing daily bread, cloth, and things.

Here are the translations:

Nakhē barchiyō bahu sāmasāmī, chālē luvāgyūn na rahē khāmī;
Salakē sāṅgy nē saṇeṇe tīr, laḍē māmhōmāhmē śūravīr. 39
